title: Profile: user can choose a language in profile settings.
steps_actions:
1. 1\. Open the app\.
2\. Tap on 'profile'\.
3\. Check the function of language changing\.
steps_result: 1. The posibillity of changing language in app is presented.

title: Registration: input correct phone number of an existing user.
preconditions: The app is installed, the user is registrated before.
steps_actions:
1. 1\. Open the app\.
2\. Tap on 'profile'\.
3\. Tap on 'registration' and input test data\.
4\. The code in message is sent to user's phone\.
5\. Input code from the message\.

title: Registration: input phone number with a short length.
steps_actions:
1. 1\. Open the app\.
2\. Tap on 'profile'\.
3\. Tap on 'registration' and input test data\.
steps_result: 1. The warning message about the short length of number is presented before clicking on "get a code".

title: Registration: input incorrect phone number with non-existing phone code.
steps_actions:
1. 1\. Open the app\.
2\. Tap on 'profile'\.
3\. Tap on 'registration' and input test data\.
steps_result: 1. The warning message 'incorrect number' is presented.

title: Registration: input a phone number with a length more than 12 numbers.
steps_actions:
1. 1\. Open the app\.
2\. Tap on 'profile'\.
3\. Tap on 'registration' and input test data\.
steps_result: 1. The user can input more than 12 numbers into the field.

title: Registration: user can be registered using e-mail.
steps_actions:
1. 1\. Open the app\.
2\. Tap on 'profile'\.
3\. Tap on 'registration' and try to input letters\.
steps_result: 1. User can input e-mail into registration field.

title: Profile: the information about delivery, pickup-points, ways of payments, product refund, money refund, rules of using and general info is presented in profile settings.
steps_actions:
1. 1\. Open the app\.
2\. Tap on 'profile'\.
3\. Check the fields are described in summary\.
steps_result: 1. The information about delivery, pickup-points, ways of payments, product refund, money refund, rules of using and general info is presented in profile settings.

title: Registration: the app suggests to log in via previous phone number after reinstalling.
steps_actions:
1. 1\. Open the app\.
2\. Tap on 'profile'\.
3\. Tap on 'registration' and confirm logging in via previous phone number\.
steps_result: 1. The user can log in after app's reinstalling without inputting phone number again.

title: Registration: user can be registered via real phone number from the country which is out from list (it's about the list of countries which cooperate with the market).
steps_actions:
1. 1\. Open the app\.
2\. Tap on 'profile'\.
3\. Tap on 'registration' and input test data\.
steps_result: 1. User can be registered via phone number from any country.
